name: Amor
description:
I made this drawing many years ago one day when I felt that everything was burning around me, I did not know what to do and the truth is that I just wanted to cry, at that moment my grandmother appeared and she hugged me until the fire ceased to exist. 

Sometimes it doesn't matter that we feel that everything is burning around us, love always fixes everything 🐶🐰
PS: We bunnies cry a lot
